SUMMARY— [Provides for a study on the treatment of trauma.] Revises
provisions relating to the designation of hospitals as centers
for the treatment of trauma. (BDR [S-153)] 40-153)
FISCAL NOTE: Effect on Local Government: May have Fiscal Impact.
Effect on the State: Yes.
